### Admin ile Login
POST https://localhost:5001/api/account/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@test.com",
  "password": "Pa$$w0rd"
}

### Normal Kullanıcı Register
POST https://localhost:5001/api/account/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User",
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "password": "Pa$$w0rd"
}

### Normal Kullanıcı Login
POST https://localhost:5001/api/account/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
