### Admin Secret (JWT token gerekli)
GET https://localhost:5001/api/buggy/admin-secret
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Kullanıcıya Admin Rolü Ver (Admin JWT token gerekli)
POST https://localhost:5001/api/account/assign-role
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "role": "Admin"
}
